      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――2017年7月24日",
      "startTime": 0.1866665999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～っ……疲れた～……",
      "startTime": 2.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-15.m4a",
      "text": "もう？　「疲れた」なんて",
      "startTime": 7.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-11.m4a",
      "text": "仕事じゃ聞いたことないのに。どうしたの？",
      "startTime": 9.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "体は疲れてない。でも、神経を使う\nそれももの凄く使う",
      "startTime": 17.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-01.m4a",
      "text": "どうして？",
      "startTime": 20.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-17.m4a",
      "text": "私達、普通に仲良く遊んでるだけだよね？",
      "startTime": 22.2371686473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈がはしゃぎ過ぎるからだぞ\nあんなに大声を出すなよ",
      "startTime": 28.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-02.m4a",
      "text": "無言でジェットコースターに乗ってる人の方が",
      "startTime": 31.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-12.m4a",
      "text": "かえって目立つと思うけどな～",
      "startTime": 34.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それだけじゃない。他のアトラクションでも騒いでたろ\n目立ち過ぎる",
      "startTime": 40.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "誰かに写真を撮られてSNSにアップされたら\nどうするんだ？",
      "startTime": 45.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-26.m4a",
      "text": "別に撮らせたらいいんじゃない？",
      "startTime": 47.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ダメだ。そんなことになったら、マスコミに\n長瀬麻奈が変な男と交際してるとか書かれて……",
      "startTime": 52.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-14.m4a",
      "text": "そしたら、この人は変な男なんかじゃありません！",
      "startTime": 56.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-09.m4a",
      "text": "――ってはっきり言うよ",
      "startTime": 60.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "俺を擁護してくれ、と言ってる訳じゃない",
      "startTime": 61.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-04.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くんはやっぱり心配し過ぎだよ～",
      "startTime": 65.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-05.m4a",
      "text": "気遣いは嬉しいけどさ",
      "startTime": 69.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_tired-03.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく今は二人で遊びに来たんだから、楽しもうよ",
      "startTime": 70.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-08.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりの休日なのは、私だけじゃなくて",
      "startTime": 74.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}くんも同じでしょ？",
      "startTime": 76.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-12.m4a",
      "text": "今日はアイドルとか、マネージャーとか",
      "startTime": 79.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-05.m4a",
      "text": "そーいうの一切なし！　OK？",
      "startTime": 81.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（……アイドルとマネージャーじゃないなら）\n（今、俺達は、どんな関係なんだ……？）",
      "startTime": 86.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（クラスメイト？　いや、ただのクラスメイト同士で）\n（二人きりで遊園地に行くのか？　分からない……）",
      "startTime": 95.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-01.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くん！　聞いてる？",
      "startTime": 100.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめん、考え事して聞いてなかった。何？",
      "startTime": 102.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_enter-01.m4a",
      "text": "私、次あそこに行きたい！",
      "startTime": 107.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "お化け屋敷……？　大丈夫なのか？\nここのは本格的って聞いてるぞ",
      "startTime": 113.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-09.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前でしょ～？\n私、お化けとか幽霊とか、全然平気だし！",
      "startTime": 118.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
